---
description: Keep tracked repository files canonical and use git mv for moves
alwaysApply: true
---

Before creating, moving, renaming, deleting, or duplicating tracked paths, use
the `organize-repository` skill from `.agents/skills/`. Follow
`docs/repository-organization.md`, search for an existing owner first, and use
`git mv` instead of `mv` for tracked relocations. Run
`python -m scripts.repo_policy` before finishing.
